  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't remember that there was any great jubilation or celebration.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Somehow, we [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] stayed together for [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] another night and then in the morning ventured out beyond the confines of this little camp and walked through the woods to the main road.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] The main road, which turned out to be the main highway from Vienna, [? road ?] number one, was extremely busy.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was a tall American soldier with a rifle, and we witnessed a motorcycle with a sidecar arriving with a German officer in the sidecar.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] American soldier asked for his gun but otherwise let the motorcycle continue on its journey, which we were extremely surprised that the Americans would let them pass rather than shoot them or intern them.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We crossed the road and were somehow following the tattered crowd, dragging ourselves to the nearest village, which was the village of Gunskirchen, and ended up near the railway station, where there was a huge storage shed or storage house that was the iron reserve, food reserve of the German army.",
      "word_count": 51
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the Allies, the Americans have opened it so that everybody could go in and take what they wanted.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were almost intermingled with us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The scene, the confusion-- and they would come to this food storage house with carts and horses and shovel the sugar and load bags of flour or whatever raw food material there was and take it away.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the Americans didn't interfere with that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] also took some food and [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] proceeded to make a fire there and try and cook something.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't remember exactly what.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
